@NODE future "The future"

@{b}Autostart :@{ub}
This is the first public release of "Autostart". I considered creating a GUI
or localizing the program, but it turned out to be rather useless (GUI with
only 3 string gadgets ? (Hopefully) never appering error messages in
different languages ???). If someone has good ideas of improving and en-
hancing "Autostart", I'd be glad to hear about them and - if it makes sense
then - add the features mentioned above.

@{b}Other projects :@{ub}
On Aminet (disk/cdrom) and on my homepage you can find my program "Discus".
This is - nomen est omen - a CD player. Yet another CD player ??? Yes,
because all other CD players I know are missing something. Here is a list
of the advantages of my program:

À   Clearly arranged + really (!) compact user interface (CD player look)
À   Commodity - Use the keyboard for the most important functions; the
    window automatically pops up whenever you insert a CD, the screen's
    title bar shows the current track
À   Full-featured ARexx port
À   Automatic recognition and display of already known CDs
À   EID file format: Allows 3 line titles and synchornizable subtitles
    (Just right for soundtracks!)
À   Title programming, random replay (combinable with title programming),
    Intro function, fading and muting
À   Multilingual using the Locale.library
@ENDNODE

